display_name: Frequency of the baby being in agony, screaming, drawing his/her legs up to his/her body, and can't be calmed
description: Has your baby ever had times when he/she appears to be in agony, screams, draws his/her legs up to his/her body, and can't be calmed? If Yes, has this happened often, sometimes, or only once?
